      "content": "hey so i made a sourdough starter like a week ago and i just fed it again yesterday but it hasn't really done anything. its been 24 hours and there are no bubbles and it hasn't grown at all. my kitchen is around 68 degrees and i'm using all purpose flour. am i doing something wrong?",
